%p
  %code
    frame_material
  is a bike attribute.

%p
  We offer these types of materials because we believe they cover all the possibilities. Please #{link_to "send us an email", "mailto:support@bikeindex.org"} if you think we're missing something!

%article.code
  %p.code-label
    GET all frame materials
  - request_url = @root + api_v1_frame_materials_path
  %pre
    :plain
      $.ajax({
        type: "GET",
        url: "#{request_url}",
        success: function(data, textStatus, jqXHR) {
          $('#frame_materials_index').text(JSON.stringify(data,undefined,2))
        }
      });
  %p.code-label Response
  %pre#frame_materials_index{ data: {url: request_url }}
    :plain